---
import SectionHeading from './SectionHeading.astro';
---

<section class="product-screens" id="screens" aria-labelledby="screens-title">
  <div class="shell">
    <SectionHeading
      id="screens-title"
      label="Inside Vaani"
      title="The product, exactly as it ships."
      description="The desktop app keeps vocabulary, writing styles, reusable phrases, and everyday controls visible without turning dictation into another workspace to manage."
    />

    <article class="screen-story screen-story--dictionary" data-reveal="scale">
      <div class="screen-copy">
        <span class="screen-index">01 / Dictionary</span>
        <h3>Your language remains recognizable.</h3>
        <p>Save exact spellings and recurring terms, then let Vaani learn repeated names and acronyms as they appear in your dictation.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="screen-frame">
        <img
          src="/product/vaani-dictionary.png"
          width="1679"
          height="1095"
          loading="lazy"
          decoding="async"
          alt="Vaani Dictionary screen for saving exact spellings and automatically learning repeated terms"
        />
      </div>
    </article>

    <div class="feature-plates">
      <article class="feature-plate" data-reveal="left">
        <div class="screen-copy">
          <span class="screen-index">02 / Style</span>
          <h3>One thought, shaped for the app in front of you.</h3>
          <p>Choose how personal messages, work messages, email, and other writing should read after transcription.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="screen-frame">
          <img
            src="/product/vaani-styles.png"
            width="1685"
            height="1108"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            alt="Vaani Style screen showing formal, casual, and very casual writing treatments"
          />
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="feature-plate feature-plate--offset" data-reveal="right" style="--reveal-delay: 60ms">
        <div class="screen-copy">
          <span class="screen-index">03 / Snippets</span>
          <h3>Repeatable details stay ready on cue.</h3>
          <p>Speak a saved phrase naturally and insert its full expansion while the surrounding dictation keeps its polish.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="screen-frame">
          <img
            src="/product/vaani-snippets.png"
            width="1682"
            height="1113"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            alt="Vaani Snippets screen for expanding spoken phrases into reusable blocks of text"
          />
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="settings-heading" data-reveal>
      <span class="screen-index">04 / Settings</span>
      <div>
        <h3>Set the behavior once. Keep speaking.</h3>
        <p>Shortcut, language, appearance, startup, sound, and notification controls stay local and explicit.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="settings-strip" aria-label="Vaani settings screens">
      <article class="settings-card" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 0ms">
        <div class="settings-card__label"><span>General</span><small>Input and language</small></div>
        <div class="screen-frame">
          <img
            src="/product/vaani-settings-general.png"
            width="1670"
            height="1027"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            alt="Vaani General settings for shortcut, microphone, dictation language, and app language"
          />
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="settings-card" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 60ms">
        <div class="settings-card__label"><span>Appearance</span><small>Window and color</small></div>
        <div class="screen-frame">
          <img
            src="/product/vaani-settings-appearance.png"
            width="1276"
            height="900"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            alt="Vaani Appearance settings for window transparency and primary interface color"
          />
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="settings-card" data-reveal style="--reveal-delay: 120ms">
        <div class="settings-card__label"><span>System</span><small>Startup and sounds</small></div>
        <div class="screen-frame">
          <img
            src="/product/vaani-settings-system.png"
            width="1267"
            height="1005"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
            alt="Vaani System settings for startup behavior, flow-bar visibility, sounds, and notifications"
          />
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .product-screens {
    padding-block: var(--space-10);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    background: var(--color-void);
  }

  .screen-story {
    margin-top: var(--space-9);
  }

  .screen-copy {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(150px, 0.45fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-5);
    align-items: start;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  .screen-copy h3,
  .settings-heading h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 3.6rem);
    font-variation-settings: 'wdth' 88;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.055em;
    line-height: 0.98;
  }

  .screen-copy p {
    grid-column: 2;
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: calc(var(--space-3) * -1) 0 0;
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
  }

  .screen-index {
    padding-top: 0.48rem;
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .screen-frame {
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-white);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 72px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.36);
    transition:
      border-color var(--duration-base) ease,
      transform var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out-strong);
  }

  .screen-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    transition: transform var(--duration-base) var(--ease-out-strong);
  }

  .feature-plates {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
  }

  .feature-plate--offset {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
  }

  .feature-plate .screen-copy {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  .feature-plate .screen-copy p {
    grid-column: 1;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .settings-heading {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(150px, 0.45fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-5);
    align-items: start;
    margin-top: var(--space-10);
    padding-top: var(--space-6);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-ink);
  }

  .settings-heading > div {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .settings-heading p {
    max-width: 650px;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
  }

  .settings-strip {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-4);
    margin-top: var(--space-7);
  }

  .settings-card__label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .settings-card__label span {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .settings-card__label small {
    color: var(--color-steel);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
  }

  :global(html.motion-ready) .settings-card[data-reveal] {
    transform: translateY(14px);
  }

  :global(html.motion-ready) .settings-card[data-reveal].is-revealed {
    transform: none;
  }

  @media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine) {
    .screen-frame:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: var(--color-steel);
    }

    .screen-frame:hover img {
      transform: scale(1.008);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .feature-plates {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .feature-plate--offset {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .settings-strip {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    }

    .settings-card:last-child {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      width: calc(50% - var(--space-2));
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 719px) {
    .screen-story {
      margin-top: var(--space-8);
    }

    .screen-copy,
    .settings-heading {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-3);
    }

    .screen-copy p {
      grid-column: 1;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .screen-frame {
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    }

    .settings-strip {
      width: calc(100vw - max(16px, calc((100vw - var(--shell)) / 2)));
      grid-auto-columns: minmax(82vw, 1fr);
      grid-template-columns: none;
      grid-auto-flow: column;
      gap: var(--space-3);
      margin-right: calc((100vw - var(--shell)) / -2);
      padding-right: 16px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      overscroll-behavior-inline: contain;
      scroll-padding-inline: 0 16px;
      scroll-snap-type: inline proximity;
      scrollbar-width: thin;
    }

    .settings-card,
    .settings-card:last-child {
      width: auto;
      scroll-snap-align: start;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    :global(html.motion-ready) .settings-card[data-reveal],
    :global(html.motion-ready) .settings-card[data-reveal].is-revealed,
    .screen-frame,
    .screen-frame img,
    .screen-frame:hover,
    .screen-frame:hover img {
      transform: none;
    }

    .screen-frame,
    .screen-frame img {
      transition-property: border-color;
      transition-duration: 180ms;
    }
  }
</style>
